# PayStream Trivy Ignore File
#
# Format: CVE-ID  # Justification: <reason>  Expires: <date>
#
# POLICY:
#   - Each entry must have a justification comment
#   - Each entry should have an expiry date for review
#   - No CVE suppressed without documented approval
#
# Example:
# CVE-2023-XXXXX  # Justification: False positive in test scope only. Expires: 2025-06-01
#
# Currently: no suppressions. All CVEs must be addressed.
